questions: Is it something humans created or invented?
Is it a natural phenomenon or force (like gravity, time, or energy)?
Is it an abstract concept or idea (like love, justice, or happiness)?
Is it a living being or entity (real or fictional/mythological)?
Is it a real biological organism that exists (or existed) on Earth?
Is it an animal (rather than a plant, fungus, bacteria, etc.)?
Is it a vertebrate animal (having a backbone/spine)?
Is it a type of mammal commonly kept as a pet (e.g., dog, cat, hamster)?
Is it a dog (or a specific breed of dog)?
